G HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/3/02 9:03:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=633.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: nothing in EQ has pissed me off this much until now</span><hr size=1> I'd believe the spdat listing over Caster's Realm's dictation of the effects.<br><br>In any case, it's not Verant's fault you didn't heed the advice of this entire board and decided to get MGB.<br><br> <p><font face="Verdana" size="-2"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=45589">Aeryl Firebrand</a>, Warlord<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65788">Aeril Droigheann</a>, 59 Preserver, Semi-Retired<br><a href="http://www.freshpope.com/undaunted/">Undaunted</a>, Xegony<br></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utudamorf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tudamorf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/3/02 9:11:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=633.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/lag999/rtfm.txt width=100 height=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: nothing in EQ has pissed me off this much until now</span><hr size=1> Caster's Realm is an extremely unreliable source for spell information, especially information about specific spell effects.  EQCaster isn't always right either, but I would certainly believe that result first.<br><br>Then again, if both spells have a mana regen effect in effect register #4, and POTG has no regeneration in #8, then the stronger effect should normally take precedence over the weaker effect if the casters are of the same level. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uglorybme.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glorybme</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.glorysite.com/eq/images3/gloryspin.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/3/02 11:33:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=633.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.glorysite.com/eq/images3/gloryb3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: nothing in EQ has pissed me off this much until now</span><hr size=1> If we have learned NOTHING else, learn that Verant will always give another class better than what we have. They toss us a bone, get us excited thinking JUST MAYBE we will become a class in demand again, only to give another class a better spell in a few months. <br><br>So many people make druids JUST to use as taxis that Verant probably thinks there are too many druids and they don't want to encourage anyone else to make a druid. Trying desperately to find an excuse for them, pitiful as it might be.<br><br>Sow, ports, buffs, snare, root, either another class has better now OR they can not be used indoors and that is what most dungeons are and where we need to be in higher levels. ALSO, they have made it extremely hard and useless to solo, yet they make most our spells most useable to only us soloing. They have cut exp for outdoor mobs, made them so they are almost or are impossible to root/snare and basically clipped our outdoor wings, forcing to become indoor creatures with nothing to contribute indoors. <p><img src=http://www.glorysite.com/eq/images2/druidsigani1.gif align=right><center><font size=3 face=georgia,arial><b>Gloria<br>